#12201
hermit~
the hermit~
The hermit of this hut sits here on the ground.
~
It's not quite what you'd have expected, some kind of ape-like creature
who evidentally is more intelligent then your average creatures.  It's built
this here hut, and lives by travelling to and from the forest for things, and
has many varities of these things from the forest lying here, perhaps you can
bargain with it for some stuff.
~
1073743873 0 0 C
12 0 0 0d0+0 0d0+0
0 0
108 108 0
13 13 13 13 13 13 13
0 0 0 0 0
21 5 0 0 0 0 0
0 15 0 0 2048 0 0 0
> greet_prog 100~
'A visitor!  What do you want?
~
> death_prog 100~
groan
if rand(20) == 1
'You haven't beaten me yet.
mpechoaround $n As the hermit draws it's last breath, it condenses it's power to strike $n dead where $e stands!
mpechoat $n With it's last breath, the hermit strikes you dead in your tracks!
mpslay $n
else
mpoload 12202 10
mpecho As the hermit dies, it drops something on the ground.
drop shield
endif
mptransfer hermit 11288
mpat 12300 mpecho The hermit's corpse returns to the earth from whence it came...
~
> act_prog p buys a match.~
mpecho _lbl The hermit says 'Now bring that match back here anytime and give it to me and I will create for you a fire.'
~
> act_prog p gives you a match.~
mpecho _lbl The hermit says 'You want a fire?  I make for you fire.'
nw
mpat 0.$n mpechoat $n You decide to follow the hermit.
mpat 0.$n mpforce $n nw
mpecho The hermit strikes the match against the side of it's leg, and the sparks fall into some dry straw, producing a lit fire.
mpoload 30 1
mptransfer hermit 12300
mpat 12242 mpecho The hermit leaves southeast.
~
|
